  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.58,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.58,
      "end": 30.68,
      "text": "영어 공부가 즐거워지는 시간 스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.68,
      "end": 37.38,
      "text": "4월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 긍정 에너지를 무한 발사하는 강아지의 특별한 모험담"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.38,
      "end": 50.9,
      "text": "우리 지난주였던 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.9,
      "end": 58.6,
      "text": "we've talked about Conrad Vernon이라는 감독에 대해서 아주 잠깐 다뤄본 적이 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.6,
      "end": 59.72,
      "text": "his personal story"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.72,
      "end": 64.32,
      "text": "이 사람의 강아지를 모델로 만들어진 영화라는 얘기도 했었는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.32,
      "end": 70.48,
      "text": "Actually, when I first heard his name, Trouble, I mean, I felt strange and weird at first"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.48,
      "end": 71.14,
      "text": "The dog's name"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.14,
      "end": 75.22,
      "text": "Trouble이라는 이름에 대해서 되게 뭔가 좀 이상하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.22,
      "end": 77.34,
      "text": "왜 이렇게 붙였을까라고 생각을 했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.34,
      "end": 82.04,
      "text": "While searching for some data, I found something interesting"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.04,
      "end": 84.24,
      "text": "Interesting? What did you find?"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.24,
      "end": 91.2,
      "text": "이게요, 실제로 엄청난 양의 유산을 받은 강아지 중에 진짜로"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.2,
      "end": 95.16,
      "text": "Trouble이라는 이름이 붙여진 강아지가 있다는 이야기를 들었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.16,
      "end": 100.32,
      "text": "In actual real life, there's a dog named Trouble that got a huge inheritance"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.32,
      "end": 102.24,
      "text": "Oh, what do you know?"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.22,
      "end": 106.52,
      "text": "But it wasn't based on this dog, but it's a real actual dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.52,
      "end": 111.54,
      "text": "So, yeah, there was an actual dog that was owned by a lady"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.54,
      "end": 117.14,
      "text": "who became very well-known for her bad behavior and her wealth"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.14,
      "end": 121.1,
      "text": "So, she was a businesswoman named Leona Helmsley"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.1,
      "end": 124.42,
      "text": "and she worked in real estate and hotels"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.42,
      "end": 125.84,
      "text": "She ran many hotels"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.84,
      "end": 130.56,
      "text": "and she developed a huge fortune of about 5 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.56,
      "end": 131.8,
      "text": "한 5조원 정도"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.8,
      "end": 133.6,
      "text": "엄청난 부자였죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.6,
      "end": 139.26,
      "text": "So, when she passed away, nobody, she had no friends or family"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.26,
      "end": 141.54,
      "text": "and she lived all alone with a dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.54,
      "end": 144.0,
      "text": "And the dog's name was Trouble"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.0,
      "end": 145.18,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.18,
      "end": 147.72,
      "text": "And she gave 12 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.72,
      "end": 149.32,
      "text": "12 million dollars?"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.42,
      "end": 150.28,
      "text": "To Trouble"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.28,
      "end": 151.7,
      "text": "12 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.7,
      "end": 152.34,
      "text": "140억?"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.52,
      "end": 153.1,
      "text": "그 정도"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.1,
      "end": 153.94,
      "text": "Oh my gosh"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.94,
      "end": 155.48,
      "text": "130, 140억 정도"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.48,
      "end": 155.96,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.96,
      "end": 158.26,
      "text": "And she had two grandchildren"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.26,
      "end": 160.66,
      "text": "But she didn't even put them in the will"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.66,
      "end": 160.78,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.0,
      "end": 162.22,
      "text": "She disinherited them"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.22,
      "end": 162.8,
      "text": "Oh my gosh"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.8,
      "end": 163.68,
      "text": "Bye-bye, grandkids"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.68,
      "end": 164.86,
      "text": "Hello, Trouble"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.86,
      "end": 165.76,
      "text": "I like you"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.76,
      "end": 166.64,
      "text": "You're my only friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.64,
      "end": 167.0,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.0,
      "end": 168.14,
      "text": "Left them a lot of money"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.14,
      "end": 168.52,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.52,
      "end": 170.16,
      "text": "A judge later said"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.16,
      "end": 171.84,
      "text": "Nah, you can't give him 12 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.84,
      "end": 174.9,
      "text": "So, he moved that amount down"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.9,
      "end": 176.38,
      "text": "To 2 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.38,
      "end": 177.1,
      "text": "To the dog?"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.52,
      "end": 178.08,
      "text": "To the dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.08,
      "end": 178.98,
      "text": "2 million"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.98,
      "end": 179.9,
      "text": "So, 25억"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.9,
      "end": 180.36,
      "text": "20억"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.36,
      "end": 182.46,
      "text": "네, 그래도 많긴 하네요, 그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.68,
      "end": 184.28,
      "text": "뭐 부자 강아지가 됐네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.28,
      "end": 184.6,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.6,
      "end": 186.8,
      "text": "He passed away a few years ago"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.8,
      "end": 189.06,
      "text": "And then all that money was donated"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.06,
      "end": 190.54,
      "text": "to dog charities"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.54,
      "end": 192.02,
      "text": "Yeah, that's a good thing"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.02,
      "end": 192.92,
      "text": "Yeah, that's a good thing"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.92,
      "end": 194.76,
      "text": "Anyway, she went to jail"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.76,
      "end": 195.6,
      "text": "She was"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.6,
      "end": 196.24,
      "text": "She had"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.24,
      "end": 197.38,
      "text": "She did tax fraud"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.38,
      "end": 198.76,
      "text": "She was not"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.76,
      "end": 200.24,
      "text": "She had a nickname"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.24,
      "end": 201.64,
      "text": "Queen of Mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.64,
      "end": 202.1,
      "text": "아, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.26,
      "end": 202.5,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.5,
      "end": 205.22,
      "text": "굉장히 negative한 nickname을 가지고 있네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.22,
      "end": 208.42,
      "text": "이 레오나라는 사람에 관련된 이야기를 들으셨는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.42,
      "end": 210.82,
      "text": "미국의 엄청난 사업가이면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.82,
      "end": 214.78,
      "text": "또 유죄 판결을 여러모로 많이 받은 사람입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.78,
      "end": 216.6,
      "text": "성격도 아주 포악했나 봐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.6,
      "end": 217.46,
      "text": "Queen of Mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.46,
      "end": 218.32,
      "text": "So mean"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.32,
      "end": 218.82,
      "text": "그러게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.82,
      "end": 221.26,
      "text": "이제 원래 강아지를 키우는 사람들이라면"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.26,
      "end": 224.18,
      "text": "좀 좋은 personality를 가지고 있을 거라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.18,
      "end": 225.44,
      "text": "선입견이 있는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.44,
      "end": 226.38,
      "text": "Not everyone"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.38,
      "end": 228.36,
      "text": "무조건 다 그런 건 아니군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.36,
      "end": 230.12,
      "text": "Hey, if you don't get along with people"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.12,
      "end": 232.48,
      "text": "Sometimes it's easier to get along with dogs"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.48,
      "end": 233.86,
      "text": "So I understand that"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.86,
      "end": 235.16,
      "text": "But, come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.16,
      "end": 236.62,
      "text": "She left your grandchildren out"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.62,
      "end": 238.3,
      "text": "Maybe they were spoiled brats"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.3,
      "end": 239.34,
      "text": "I don't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.34,
      "end": 240.0,
      "text": "그럴 수 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.0,
      "end": 240.4,
      "text": "Anyway"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.4,
      "end": 242.72,
      "text": "네, 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.72,
      "end": 245.12,
      "text": "So pick me up off the street"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.12,
      "end": 246.08,
      "text": "I had no choice"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.08,
      "end": 246.64,
      "text": "Yeah, well"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.64,
      "end": 247.8,
      "text": "Don't get too attached"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.8,
      "end": 249.72,
      "text": "Humans will kick you out the door"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.72,
      "end": 250.92,
      "text": "Any chance they get"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.92,
      "end": 253.78,
      "text": "Do not trust them for a second"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.78,
      "end": 254.32,
      "text": "What?"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.74,
      "end": 256.54,
      "text": "No human would ever treat me badly"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.54,
      "end": 259.06,
      "text": "Then how come you're standing in the dark"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.06,
      "end": 260.46,
      "text": "In the freezing cold"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.46,
      "end": 262.86,
      "text": "Next to a pile of garbage cans"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.86,
      "end": 266.13,
      "text": "아니, trouble이요"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.13,
      "end": 270.21,
      "text": "He's just learned how to wipe his butt from his friends"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.21,
      "end": 270.75,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.91,
      "end": 271.93,
      "text": "How to wipe his butt?"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.63,
      "end": 274.11,
      "text": "예전에는 정말"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.11,
      "end": 276.07,
      "text": "He didn't even know that"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.07,
      "end": 277.23,
      "text": "He never wiped his butt"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.23,
      "end": 277.85,
      "text": "그러니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.85,
      "end": 278.15,
      "text": "항상"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.15,
      "end": 279.69,
      "text": "Did someone wipe his butt for him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.07,
      "end": 282.69,
      "text": "아니요, 대신 향수를 뿌려줬다고 그랬어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.69,
      "end": 285.61,
      "text": "Yes, a little cologne in the butt"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.61,
      "end": 286.75,
      "text": "Perfume"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.75,
      "end": 287.77,
      "text": "근데 하필이면 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.77,
      "end": 290.19,
      "text": "그 공원에 있었던 강아지들한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.19,
      "end": 291.19,
      "text": "막 배워가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.19,
      "end": 294.99,
      "text": "그거를 조의의 집에서 하고 있다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.99,
      "end": 299.35,
      "text": "She left him outside her house at night"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.35,
      "end": 300.71,
      "text": "걔 공원에서 했던 걸"
    },
    {
      "start": 300.71,
      "end": 301.75,
      "text": "집에서 하니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.75,
      "end": 302.89,
      "text": "Hey, you're out!"
    },
    {
      "start": 302.99,
      "end": 303.37,
      "text": "Get out!"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.51,
      "end": 303.75,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.75,
      "end": 305.61,
      "text": "그리고 나서는 지금"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.61,
      "end": 307.89,
      "text": "He met Rousey again"
    },
    {
      "start": 307.89,
      "end": 308.87,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.87,
      "end": 312.67,
      "text": "근데 Rousey가 쓰레기통을 막 뒤지고 있었던 장면이었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.67,
      "end": 313.99,
      "text": "He's dumpster diving"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.99,
      "end": 315.51,
      "text": "Looking for food"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.51,
      "end": 315.85,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.85,
      "end": 320.63,
      "text": "어떤 단어들이 있었는지 한번 살펴볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.33,
      "end": 323.13,
      "text": "Don't get too attached"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.13,
      "end": 327.17,
      "text": "네, 정을 너무 많이 주지 마라는 문장입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.17,
      "end": 329.75,
      "text": "이게 동사 부분만 나와 있는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.75,
      "end": 332.27,
      "text": "정을 너무 많이 주지 마라는 것을"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.27,
      "end": 334.11,
      "text": "Don't get too attached"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.11,
      "end": 335.63,
      "text": "라는 표현을 쓴 거거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.63,
      "end": 338.65,
      "text": "특히 attached라는 단어를 보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.65,
      "end": 341.17,
      "text": "A-T-T-A-C-H라고 해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.17,
      "end": 344.13,
      "text": "붙이다, 첨부하다, 들러붙다"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.13,
      "end": 345.01,
      "text": "라는 의미인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.01,
      "end": 348.09,
      "text": "그래서 소위 attachment라고 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.09,
      "end": 350.59,
      "text": "첨부 파일이라는 의미로도 쓰일 수가 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.59,
      "end": 351.11,
      "text": "Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.11,
      "end": 353.09,
      "text": "File attached to an email"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.09,
      "end": 353.41,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.41,
      "end": 354.35,
      "text": "아니면은"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.35,
      "end": 357.07,
      "text": "Sometimes affection이라는 의미로도 쓰일 수 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.07,
      "end": 357.85,
      "text": "Of course"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.85,
      "end": 359.79,
      "text": "If you watch someone else's dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.79,
      "end": 361.35,
      "text": "Babysit a dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.35,
      "end": 363.29,
      "text": "Sometimes you can grow attached"
    },
    {
      "start": 363.29,
      "end": 364.69,
      "text": "But don't get too attached"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.69,
      "end": 366.05,
      "text": "Because you have to return the dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.05,
      "end": 366.39,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.39,
      "end": 369.33,
      "text": "이 애착 혹은 정이라는 의미로"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.33,
      "end": 371.31,
      "text": "attachment 혹은 affection"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.31,
      "end": 373.03,
      "text": "이라는 단어를 쓸 수 있겠구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.03,
      "end": 374.79,
      "text": "라는 생각까지 하게 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.79,
      "end": 377.05,
      "text": "정을 너무 많이 붙이지 마"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.05,
      "end": 379.47,
      "text": "정을 너무 많이 주지 마라는 표현이었어요"
